{"tid":644542,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人由心底覺得自己好廢","createTime":"2018-04-27T10:09:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-27T16:11:24.000Z","uid":6005,"like":23,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"67721d6d8c1895e4ddb8d7cfb1bb207fc5b1993f","tid":644542,"uid":6005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T10:09:23.000Z","msg":"聽首歌仔先<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/RQTOO4M3Hh8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FRQTOO4M3Hh8&d=Cafjcg0goWczJSZ7u65liY9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=0c26d20d\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/RQTOO4M3Hh8</a><br />\n<br />\n真係從心底都覺得自己好撚廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  ，都成幾十歲人，唔好話有咩專長，連自己一樣興趣都搵唔到。<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 做咩野都淨係識得拖，拖到最後一刻先會去做，甚至最後連做都唔會做，就算明知係對自己有好處，都係冇勇氣，冇膽去做，仲會同自己搵籍口，話下次先啦，但自己明知係唔會有下一次機會，正如達哥話「懦夫，連幸福都害怕，棉花也會受傷」，都唔知自己因為害怕而放棄左幾多機會。<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n希望各位巴絲打唔好好似我咁，比自己嘅人生留低咁多遺憾。<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：張敬軒打手"},{"pid":"4e5926ebaae9977461138e115c49217715b96b23","tid":644542,"uid":6005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T10:23:34.000Z","msg":"廢都連post都冇人覆<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ee5a8a118775961ae6d3548a1ec487421395e19","tid":644542,"uid":145247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T10:26:17.000Z","msg":"Rip <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62c7265331a588001cd4527371a3ac038a7c045e","tid":644542,"uid":15483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1